    "markdown": "<p>Implement a simple masonry grid layout using HTML and CSS.</p><p>### Requirements\n1. Use Tailwind CSS for styling.\n2. The grid items should be of varying heights.\n3. The grid should be responsive and work on different screen sizes.\n4. Add some sample images to the grid.</p>"
